<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    />
    <link rel="icon" href="https://cse135.monster/favicon_io/favicon.ico" />

    <title>User CRUD</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.zinggrid.com/zinggrid.min.js"></script>
    <style>
      body {
        background: #e6e6e6;
      }

      zg-cell {
        height: "200";
        max-height: "200";
        vertical-align: top;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="text-center mt-5">Users Information</h1>
      <h2>
        Important: To add a new user, you shouldn't manually set user id. Just leave it empty. If you want to insert with a certain id, please make sure it's not deplicated.
      </h2>
      <p>
        The <b>admin</b> field should be set to either <b>0</b> or <b>1</b>. 0 means the user is not an admin, 1 means the user is an admin.
      </p>
      <p>
        To partial update a user (PATCH), click on a certain cell and edit it. Then, press enter. 
      </p>
      <p>
        To entirely update a user (PUT), click the '+' button. 
      </p>
      <p>
        Password is hashed using bcrypt. 
      </p>
      <zing-grid
        caption="Users"
        compact=""
        zebra=""
        role="grid"
        viewport="tablet-portrait"
        editor-controls
        layout-controls
        pager
        page-size="5"
        src="/usercrud"
        class="mt-4",
        style="width: 100%"
      >
      </zing-grid>
      <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary">Back</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
